reviewText: I have found this a singularly entertaining and wonderfully organized complete addition of YTJD.  While I haven't listened to every single episode, practically all of the 5 part episodes are in great shape and are well preserved.  I am grateful to have found this, and recommend it to all of my fellow old time radio fans.

shameful quality
